    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? This beauty has been my absolute pride and joy, kept in a climate-controlled garage and pampered like a member of the family. Seriously, it\u2019s in flawless condition\u2014not a single scratch or dent to be found! It drives like a dream and still has that fresh new-car smell inside. I'm honestly sad to see it go, but I know it'll make its next owner so happy. Come take a look and fall in love!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
