      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S is a peerless example of the 996.2 generation, featuring the naturally aspirated 3.6L flat-six M96/03 powerplant delivering linear torque through a precise 6-speed longitudinal manual transaxle. The wide-body chassis, shared with the Turbo variant, integrates a viscous multi-plate clutch all-wheel-drive system and a factory-tuned suspension with optimized geometry and reinforced anti-roll bars. Deceleration is managed by four-piston monobloc calipers over cross-drilled, ventilated rotors, ensuring zero fade. This specimen maintains exacting factory tolerances, with a surgically clean engine bay and a pristine undercarriage. It is a mechanically superlative driver\u2019s car for the discerning purist seeking peak analog performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
