    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true showroom-quality masterpiece that defies its age. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in an exterior with a deep, mirror-like luster and absolutely zero imperfections\u2014no stone chips, door dings, or swirl marks. The interior is a time capsule; the hand-stitched leather retains its original suppleness and factory scent, with no visible wear on the bolsters or carpets. Every switch, dial, and screen operates with the crisp precision of a new car. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by master technicians. This car drives with tight, responsive handling and a whisper-quiet cabin, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from its first day on the road. For the collector or enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is the definitive example of the model.",
      "price": 48500.0,
